data.description: If you're searching for an updated house on 3/4 acres then this well maintained, bright, open plan brick home is for you! Set on a large lot, country feel, yet still a short drive to Huntsville, Madison & all the entertainment and work areas. This recently updated home has beautiful easy clean LPV floors, a large kitchen that you can still add your finishing touches to, a new 8x4.5 walk-in pantry, ISOLATED Master bedroom with vaulted ceilings and bathroom, separate laundry room, open living and foyer with a fireplace and vaulted ceilings. The lot has some beautiful trees, a detached workshop or oversized 2 car garage and a circular driveway. Back porch overlooking your property & firepit.
